sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NAME , COURSEalias0.NUMBER , INSTRUCTORalias0.NAME FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 INNER JOIN COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 ON COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID INNER JOIN SEMESTER AS SEMESTERalias0 ON SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SEMESTER INNER JOIN PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 ON PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID INNER JOIN OFFERING_INSTRUCTOR AS OFFERING_INSTRUCTORalias0 ON OFFERING_INSTRUCTORalias0.OFFERING_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.OFFERING_ID INNER JOIN INSTRUCTOR AS INSTRUCTORalias0 ON OFFERING_INSTRUCTORalias0.INSTRUCTOR_ID = INSTRUCTORalias0.INSTRUCTOR_ID WHERE PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.CATEGORY LIKE "MDE" AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER = "WN" AND SEMESTERalias0.YEAR = 2017 ;
